PAGE FOUR
RECORD AND REPLAY
SPACE: Return to Saving And Loading PAGE
R: Record
P: Replay
A: Replay all saved
   First of all, You should know You can swich between
Duenix and other tasks in THIS page. You can do it by
pressing LAmiga & A.
 
  When You press C, You will be asked the path of file
that will be used as config list. In this file should
be listed the names of config files You want to have
in User gameset. These can be up to 20 and should be
stored in the same drawer as config list was.
  After that User gameset will be created from these
configs and will be saved to drawer, where all Duenix
files are stored. Since than, you will  be able  to
access configurations from gameset by pressing S and
then U in main game page.
